replyContent:
Hello!
If you have already received the refund for the purchased app, you'll have to purchase it again if you want to play it. When you purchase an app, it is added to your library of purchased apps, and you can easily find it in your account. We advise you to use the library to download the purchased apps to avoid mistakes.
Regards,
FIVE-BN Games
